---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import { ArrowUpRight } from "@lucide/astro"
import BenDavis from "@/assets/avatars/BenDavis.jpg"
import Twitter from "@/assets/logos/twitter/Twitter.svg"
---

<section id="coding-with-ai" class="relative w-full py-24 md:pt-40 md:pb-24">
  <!-- Subtle gradient background -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-primary-foreground/0 via-primary-foreground/0 to-card/50"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-295">
    <div class="mb-6 md:mb-20 px-4 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start md:gap-6">
      <div>
        <p
          class="mb-3 font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground"
        >
          // LLMs ❤️ Effect
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl leading-tight font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">
          Build Agentic Systems
        </h2>
        <p class="max-w-2xl mt-4 text-xl text-muted-foreground">
          Effect's declarative patterns and strong type system make it easier for LLMs to generate
          correct, production-ready code.
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4 lg:mt-8">
          <a
            href="https://www.effect.solutions/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-zinc-900/50 hover:bg-zinc-800 text-white text-sm font-medium border border-zinc-700 hover:border-zinc-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 rounded-md no-underline group"
          >
            <span>Quick start LLM guide</span>
            <ArrowUpRight class="size-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative mt-6 md:mt-0 p-5 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-700/70 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 hover:border-zinc-700/80 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-pointer group"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <Image class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full object-cover" src={BenDavis} alt="Ben Davis" />
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Ben Davis</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">@davis7</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <Twitter class="size-4" fill="currentColor" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-muted-foreground">@MichaelArnaldi</span> suggested cloning the effect repo
          as a git subtree, giving it to Claude, then using that as docs. It sounds absurd, but it's actually
          kind amazing...
        </p>
        <a
          class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground after:absolute after:content-[''] after:-inset-px after:z-1 no-underline"
          href="https://x.com/davis7/status/1988847914538672262"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Full post <ArrowUpRight class="size-3" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground">01</span>
          <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-medium text-white">Predictable structure: </span>
            <span>every operation follows a declarative pattern, no guesswork for LLMs.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground">02</span>
          <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-medium text-white">Typed feedback loop: </span>
            <span>detailed error traces show what failed, enabling precise self-repair.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground">03</span>
          <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-medium text-white">Built-in reliability: </span>
            <span>error handling, supervision, and recovery, production-ready by default.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground">04</span>
          <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-medium text-white">Rich toolbox: </span>
            <span>from schema validation to workflows, build in a language LLMs understand.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
